<p><b>Hasbro Inc.</b> (formerly <b>Hassenfeld Brothers</b>) is an <a href="United_States.html" title="United States">American</a> <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Multinational_corporation" title="Multinational corporation">multinational</a> <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Toy" title="Toy">toy</a> and <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Board_game" title="Board game">board game</a> company. It is one of the largest toy makers in the world. The corporate headquarters is located in <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pawtucket,_Rhode_Island" title="Pawtucket, Rhode Island">Pawtucket, Rhode Island</a>. The majority of its products are manufactured in <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/East_Asia" title="East Asia">East Asia</a>.</p>
<p></p>
